    "PageTitle": "ospfv3 mtu-ignore",
    "FuncDef": "The ospfv3 mtu-ignore command disables the MTU check on DD packets.\nThe undo ospfv3 mtu-ignore command restores the default configuration.\nBy default, the MTU check on DD packets is enabled.",
